trace.description: Trace is a minimalistic logger for your Dart & Flutter projects, that uses AnsiX to print customizable messages in terminal and export log files.

ansix.description: AnsiX is a powerful and easy-to-use library that provides tools and extensions for adding ANSI color and styling support to your Dart & Flutter applications.
